# Logging Rules

- Emit structured JSON logs to stdout.
- Include `event_type`, `severity`, `request_id`, and `user_email` when applicable.
- Use required event types: `http.request`, `db.operation`, `http.outbound`, `auth.event`, `authz.decision`.
- Every outbound HTTP call must use [outbound_http.py](mdc:apps/api/src/api/outbound_http.py).
- Every authorization check must log a decision using [audit.py](mdc:apps/api/src/api/audit.py).
